name: Header Validation

steps.name: And  enter Password and launch Workbench
$("By.xpath: //h2[text()='Verify with your password']//following::input[1]") should be([exist, 10 s.])
And  scroll down the page to verify header
And  navigate to All Cases and verify header
$("By.xpath: (//td[@class='MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body MuiTableCell-sizeMedium css-e4rusy'])[1]") should be([exist, 10 s.])
And  navigate to Workbasket and verify header
$("By.xpath: (//td[@class='MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body MuiTableCell-sizeMedium css-e4rusy'])[1]") should be([exist, 10 s.])
And  navigate to Pending and verify header
$("By.xpath: (//td[@class='MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body MuiTableCell-sizeMedium css-e4rusy'])[1]") should be([exist, 10 s.])
And  navigate to Issued & Reported Cases and verify header
$("By.xpath: (//td[@class='MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body MuiTableCell-sizeMedium css-e4rusy'])[1]") should be([exist, 10 s.])
And  navigate to Inactive and verify header
$("By.xpath: (//td[@class='MuiTableCell-root MuiTableCell-body MuiTableCell-sizeMedium css-e4rusy'])[1]") should be([exist, 10 s.])
And  open every menu item in new tab and validate header
And  validate tooltip text for all menu items
Then  perform sort filter with smith and complete header validation
And  perform export and validate header
$("By.xpath: //p[contains(text(),'Exporting a csv file with ')]") get text()

fullName: UI Validation for workbench: Header Validation
